  <brief_title>Capsimax Effect on Metabolic Rate, Satiety and Food Intake</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Study of the Effect of a Dietary Herbal Supplement Containing Capsaicin or Placebo on Satiety, Metabolic Rate and Food Intake in Healthy Adults.</official_title>
